item.title: Things I Liked in 2020 (So far)
item.description: This year has been something. Still though, I want to start of this blogging thing on a good note. So, here is a compilation of things that I got to enjoy in 2020 so far. Programming Talks # Every once and a while I go on a tech talk binge. Below are some of my recent favorites. Some I have watched for the first time in this year regardless of when they came out.
